@host = http://localhost:5038
@apiKey = reminder-hemlig-123

### Skapa en påminnelse
POST {{host}}/api/reminders
Content-Type: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "loanId": 1,
  "itemId": 1,
  "itemTitle": "Testbok",
  "dueDate": "2025-12-01T00:00:00Z",
  "isSent": false
}

### Hämta alla påminnelser
GET {{host}}/api/reminders
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Räkna försenade
GET {{host}}/api/reminders/overdue/count
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}